{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"code":[" If a text's language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out vertically."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","symbolKind":"case","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","role":"symbol","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","abstract":[],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}}}